 TEIform=\"biblScope\">809b9</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n58853.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">smart, clever, ingenious</tr_>, of persons or their words and acts, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ πρῶτος εὑρὼν κ. ἦν τραγήματα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0402.tlg001:185\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Alex.\">Alex.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">185</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κ. θεαταί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0434.tlg001:169\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Cratin.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">169</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0434.tlg001:307\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">307</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Θηραμένης ὁ κ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg009.perseus-grc1:967\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ra.\">Ra.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">967</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Σικελὸς κ. ἀνήρ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0265.tlg001:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Timocr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg023:493a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Grg.\">Grg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">493a</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κ. περί τ